room_title: Escape room "Cold War Sleeper Agent" by Gateway Escape Rooms in St. Louis
room_address: 150 Concord Plaza Shopping Center Sappington, MO 63128
room_description: An urgent call from the CIA has you and your team sifting through the basement office of a recently arrested sleeper agent from the Cold War. Your job is to discover the secrets this spy has been hiding all these years. Will you be able to finish your mission before disaster strikes?
